    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Since we received Your life, Lord, a seed’s been growing there:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The seed of inward glory, the glory we will share!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By growing ’til the blossom of glory blooms in full,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll thus enjoy Your increase and glory bountiful."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hail! Captain of Salvation! Our heav’nly Pioneer!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our praises, midst the battle and tumult, You will hear."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re following our Captain all through the mighty fray."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our glorious, faithful Captain sustains us all the way."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, fighting on to glory, You now have gone before;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now fighting in Your footsteps we’ll conquer o’er and o’er."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From glory unto glory, we’ll fight until we see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The glory from within us shall manifested be."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then, Lord, at last the fighting and battle cry will cease,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we’ll appear in glory, Your kingdom and increase."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That day we’ll be completed, that day Your face we’ll see,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For in that blessed day, Lord, we’ll in the glory be!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
